  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MessageReceiver
    Interface for the Communication Layer, to be able to deliver Asynchronous messages.
    MessageSender
    Interface to be implemented by artifacts capable of sending a message to a remote ASG, and used by dose classes that need to send messages to remote peers.
